DERIVATIVE DATA NOTICE

The data in `veri/nephron_veritabani.parquet` is derived from the Layton/Hu
human nephron mathematical model (Hu et al. 2021). The MODEL itself is from:

  Hu, R., et al. (2021). Sex differences in solute and water handling in the
  human kidney. iScience 24(6):102694.
  https://doi.org/10.1016/j.isci.2021.102694

  Model code: Stadt, M., Layton, A.T. — https://github.com/mstadt/nephron

When citing this work, please cite BOTH this project AND the original Hu 2021 paper.

